Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN END if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off IF iBeamType <> BEAM_STRAIGHT THEN angy=0
pen gs_cont_pen resol gs_resol
Unid=1
!!! *** Length
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
ROTx angy
!!! *** Flange Width (Bottom)
HOTSPOT 0, -FlangeWBottom/2, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, FlangeWBottom/2, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, -FlangeWBottom/2, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, FlangeWBottom/2, 0, unID : unID=unID+1
!!! *** Total Height and Flange Width (Top)
h1 = ZZYZX h2 = ZZYZX IF iBeamType = BEAM_STRAIGHT THEN HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, ZZYZX, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, -1, unID, ZZYZX, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID, ZZYZX, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, -FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, -FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX, unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF iBeamType = BEAM_STRAIGHT OR iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED THEN HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID, ZZYZX, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, -1, unID, ZZYZX, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, ZZYZX, unID, ZZYZX, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED_2WAY THEN HOTSPOT A/2, 0, 0, unID, ZZYZX, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, -1, unID, ZZYZX, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, ZZYZX, unID, ZZYZX, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
!!! *** End Height and Flange Width (Top)
IF iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED | iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED_2WAY THEN h1 = ZZYZX2 HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, ZZYZX2, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, -1, unID, ZZYZX2, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX2, unID, ZZYZX2, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, -FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX2, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX2, unID : unID=unID+1
IF iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED_2WAY THEN h2 = ZZYZX2 HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID, ZZYZX2, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, -1, unID, ZZYZX2, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, ZZYZX2, unID, ZZYZX2, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A, -FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX2, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, FlangeWTop/2, ZZYZX2, unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF ENDIF
UnIDTmp = UnID !!! Compatibility requirement - New hotspots UnID = 200
!!! >>> Width (Bottom) HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-FlangeWBottom2,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,1,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,FlangeWBottom2,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-FlangeWBottom2,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,1,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,FlangeWBottom2,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Width (Top) HOTSPOT A,0,h2,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-FlangeWTop2,h2,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,1,h2,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,h2,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,FlangeWTop2,h2,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,h2,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,h1,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-FlangeWTop2,h1,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,1,ZZYZX,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,h1,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,FlangeWTop2,h1,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1,h1,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
UnID = UnIDTmp
ROTy 90 ROTz 90 MATERIAL gs_rbeam_mat
if Shape=1 then if gs_shap_m = HOLE_RECTANGULAR then gosub "holeRectangular" endif
if gs_shap_m = HOLE_CIRCULAR then gosub "holeCircular" endif del 1 endif
IF iBeamType = BEAM_STRAIGHT OR iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED THEN if iBeamType = BEAM_STRAIGHT then ZZYZX2 = ZZYZX if supor then addz a roty 90 cutpolya 5, 2, 0, -1,0,15, supowr,0,15, supowr,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, -1,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, -1,0,-1 del 2 endif
if supol then roty 90 cutpolya 5, 2, 0, 1,0,15, -supowl,0,15, -supowl,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, 1,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, 1,0,-1 del 1 endif
method = 1 dimA = A
else
if supor then addz a roty 90 cutpolya 5, 2, 0, -1,0,15, supowr,0,15, supowr,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, -1,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, -1,0,-1 del 2 endif
if supol then roty 90 cutpolya 5, 2, 0, 1,0,15, -supowl,0,15, -supowl,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, 1,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,15, 1,0,-1 del 1 endif
method = 2 dimA = A/2 endif
for i = 1 to method ruled 14,1+2+4+16, FlangeWBottom/2,0,0, FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom,0, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,0, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2,0, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2+SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1,0, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop,0, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2,0, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2,0, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop,0, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2-SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1,0, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2,0, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,0, -FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom,0, -FlangeWBottom/2,0,0, FlangeWBottom/2,0,dimA, FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom,dimA, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,dimA, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2,dimA, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2+SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1,dimA, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop,dimA, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX,dimA, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX,dimA, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop,dimA, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2-SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1,dimA, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2,dimA, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom,dimA, -FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom,dimA, -FlangeWBottom/2,0,dimA
rotx 180 rotz 180 addz -A next i del method * 3
if supol then cutend if supor then cutend
if Shape=1 then for i=1 to hnum if gs_shap_m = HOLE_RECTANGULAR then cutend if gs_shap_m = HOLE_CIRCULAR then cutend next i endif
DEL 2 DEL 1
END
"holeRectangular": addz -((a+0.02)/(hnum))/2 addy pos roty 90 for i=1 to hnum HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, gs_hole_pos[i], 1+128 :unID=unID+1 !!base HOTSPOT 1, 0, 0, unID, gs_hole_pos[i], 3 :unID=unID+1 !!lgth ref HOTSPOT -gs_hole_pos[i], 0, 0, unID, gs_hole_pos[i], 2 :unID=unID+1 !!lgth mov addx -gs_hole_pos[i]-rectw/2 cutpolya 4, 2, 0, 0,0,15, rectw,0,15, rectw,recth,15, 0,recth,15 del 1 next i del 2 return
"holeCircular": addz -((a+0.02)/(hnum))/2 addy pos roty 90 for i=1 to hnum HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, gs_hole_pos[i], 1+128 :unID=unID+1 !!base HOTSPOT 1, 0, 0, unID, gs_hole_pos[i], 3 :unID=unID+1 !!lgth ref HOTSPOT -gs_hole_pos[i], 0, 0, unID, gs_hole_pos[i], 2 :unID=unID+1 !!lgth mov addx -gs_hole_pos[i] addy cdia/2 cutpolya 2, 2, 0, 0,0,979, cdia/2,360,4079 del 2 next i del 2 return
Symbol.Script_2D:
if iBeamType <> BEAM_STRAIGHT then angy=0
Unid=1 hLineID = 1000
! --- Length ---
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Length/2 ---
HOTSPOT2 A/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1
FlangeWidthMax=MAX(FlangeWBottom,FlangeWTop) FlangeWidthMin=MIN(FlangeWBottom,FlangeWTop)
if only_axis=0 AND ABS(angy)<EPS then ! --- Flange Width (MAX) HOTSPOT2 0,FlangeWidthMax/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-FlangeWidthMax/2,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,FlangeWidthMax/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-FlangeWidthMax/2,unID : unID=unID+1
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then ! --- Flange Width (MIN) HOTSPOT2 0,FlangeWidthMin/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-FlangeWidthMin/2,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,FlangeWidthMin/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-FlangeWidthMin/2,unID : unID=unID+1
! --- Web Thickness HOTSPOT2 0,WebThk/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-WebThk/2,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,WebThk/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-WebThk/2,unID : unID=unID+1 endif endif
!!! *** Width IF ABS(angy)<EPS AND only_axis=0 THEN !! angy=0 IF iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED THEN UnIDTmp = UnID !!! Compatibility requirement - New hotspots UnID = 200
!!! >>> Width (Bottom) HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-FlangeWBottom2,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,1,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,FlangeWBottom2,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-1,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-FlangeWBottom2,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,1,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,FlangeWBottom2,1+128, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,FlangeWBottom2,unID,FlangeWBottom2,2, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-1,unID,FlangeWBottom2,3, FlangeWBottom : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Width (Top) HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-FlangeWTop2,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,1,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,FlangeWTop2,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-1,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-FlangeWTop2,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,1,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,FlangeWTop2,1+128, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,FlangeWTop2,unID,FlangeWTop2,2, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-1,unID,FlangeWTop2,3, FlangeWTop : unID=unID+1
UnID = UnIDTmp ENDIF ENDIF
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
if ABS(angy)<EPS then !!! >>> angy=0 ADD2 0, -FlangeWidthMax/2
if only_axis=0 then
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, A, 0, 1, a, FlangeWidthMax, 1, 0, FlangeWidthMax, 1, 0, 0, -1
if iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED_2WAY then if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then LINE2 A/2,FlangeWidthMax/2+FlangeWTop/2,A/2,FlangeWidthMax/2-FlangeWTop/2 else LINE2 A/2,0,A/2,FlangeWidthMax endif endif
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then
LINE_TYPE DetailLineType LINE2 0,FlangeWidthMax/2+WebThk/2,a,FlangeWidthMax/2+WebThk/2 LINE2 0,FlangeWidthMax/2-WebThk/2,a,FlangeWidthMax/2-WebThk/2 LINE_TYPE 1
if FlangeWBottom>FlangeWTop then LINE_TYPE 1 else LINE_TYPE DetailLineType endif
LINE2 0,FlangeWidthMax/2+FlangeWidthMin/2,a,FlangeWidthMax/2+FlangeWidthMin/2 LINE2 0,FlangeWidthMax/2-FlangeWidthMin/2,a,FlangeWidthMax/2-FlangeWidthMin/2
LINE_TYPE 1 endif endif
DEL 1 else if only_axis=0 then PROJECT2{2} 3, 270, 3+32, gs_back_pen,0,0,0 endif endif
if showsect AND only_axis=0 then LINE_TYPE 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, pos_2Dx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -1', unID, pos_2Dx, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 pos_2Dx, 0, unID, pos_2Dx, 2 : unID=unID+1 ADD2 pos_2Dx, 0 ROT2 90+angy
if iBeamType = BEAM_STRAIGHT then ZZYZX2=ZZYZX
FILL cross_fill POLY2 14,7, FlangeWBottom/2,0, FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2+SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2-SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX2-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom, -FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom, -FlangeWBottom/2,0
if iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED | iBeamType = BEAM_INCLINED_2WAY then
POLY2 14,1, FlangeWBottom/2,0, FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2, FlangeWBottom/2-(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2+SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop, FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX, -FlangeWTop/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2-SlopeHgtTop2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,ZZYZX-FlangeHgtTop-SlopeHgtTop1-SlopeHgtTop2, -FlangeWBottom/2+(FlangeWBottom-WebThk)/2,FlangeHgtBottom+SlopeHgtBottom, -FlangeWBottom/2,FlangeHgtBottom, -FlangeWBottom/2,0 endif DEL 2 endif
if axis then PEN axis_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type HOTLINE2 0, 0, a, 0, hLineID LINE2 0, 0, a, 0 endif
if Shape=1 then PEN gs_cont_pen add2 -((a+0.02)/(hnum))/2,0
for i=1 to hnum add2 gs_hole_pos[i],0
line2 0,-b/2-.07,0,b/2+.07 del 1 next i
if iHoleContour2D = HOLECONTOUR2D_ON then if gs_shap_m = HOLE_RECTANGULAR then holeOffset = rectw else holeOffset = cdia endif
add2 -holeOffset/2, 0 for i=1 to hnum add2 gs_hole_pos[i],0
line2 0,-FlangeWTop/2, 0,FlangeWTop/2 line2 holeOffset,-FlangeWTop/2, holeOffset,FlangeWTop/2
del 1 next i del 1 endif endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
!iObjectCode PRE_BEAM_I_2 = 4
rrr = request("Working_length_unit", "", w_units_form) bMetricDimension = strstr(w_units_form, "m") ! m, cm, mm
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iHoleContour2D HOLECONTOUR2D_OFF = 1 HOLECONTOUR2D_ON = 2
EPS = 0.0001
dim stBeamType[3] stBeamType[1] = `Прямой` stBeamType[2] = `Наклон с Одной Стороны` stBeamType[3] = `Наклон с Двух Сторон`
BEAM_STRAIGHT = 1 BEAM_INCLINED = 2 BEAM_INCLINED_2WAY = 3
dim stHoleShape[2] stHoleShape[1] = `Прямоугольный` stHoleShape[2] = `Круглая`
HOLE_RECTANGULAR = 1 HOLE_CIRCULAR = 2
!!Change distance between ds holes!! IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "hnum" THEN FOR i=1 TO hnum PARAMETERS gs_hole_pos[i]=(i)*(a/hnum) NEXT i ENDIF

dy = 24 yEnd = 266 pageStartY = 0 yCurrent = pageStartY + 1

if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE then lock "DetailLineType" endif
